item.title: CVE-2018-25095|2024-08-05T12:33:47.807Z -- unknown -- duplicator
item.description: The Duplicator WordPress plugin before 1.3.0 does not properly escape values when its installer script replaces values in WordPress configuration files. If this installer script is left on the site after use, it could be use to run arbitrary code on the server.
